meta.title: Webdev
meta.summary: Listing out my misc notes in article form.

content:
Featured

I have a bunch of notes on random things I catalog here.

The article contents may stray from the page title.

Contact charles.karpati@gmail.com should you have any revisions, questions, comments, or concerns!


Carlos Wp – A collection of notes and resources related to the Carlos WP project. Notes


Meta Quest Notes – Insights and observations gathered from working with Meta Quest. Notes


Openaichatgpt3 – Documentation and resources on OpenAI's GPT-3, its capabilities, and implementations. Notes


Openainotes – Detailed notes on OpenAI's offerings, technologies, and research. Notes


Stickynotes – Information and notes on the Stickynotes tool and its uses. Notes


Termux Notes – Resources and configurations related to the Termux terminal emulator. Notes


Visualization Notes – Guidelines and examples for creating effective visualizations in data analysis. Notes


Vpn – A detailed guide on using VPN services and their applications for secure connections. Notes


Cloudflare – Notes on Cloudflare's services, including security, CDN, and DNS management. Notes


Css – Comprehensive resources on CSS, styling techniques, and best practices for web design. Notes


Descriptions – A collection of text descriptions and documentation for various web development projects. Notes


DevOps – Insights into DevOps practices, tools, and workflows for modern software development. Notes


Generators – Guides and resources for using generators in web development to automate and streamline tasks. Notes


Google – Documentation and resources related to Google technologies, tools, and platforms. Notes


Misc – A collection of miscellaneous notes on various web development topics. Notes


Ml – Machine Learning concepts, libraries, and tutorials for applying ML techniques in web development. Notes


React – In-depth notes and resources on React, including its features and how to build dynamic web applications. Notes


Tutorials – A selection of tutorials covering various web development topics and technologies. Notes


Js – JavaScript resources, techniques, and best practices for web development. Notes


Html – Detailed notes on HTML, its elements, structure, and usage in web development. Notes
